parameters:
Bunny-chan: That was fun, wasn't it? Hijacking the show! I'm
not sure if the talent will be able to recover, though...

Memimi: She must have had a good time, and even if she
retires from being a talent, she's made more than enough!
After all, she got to do it live with Lord Shark Duke...
fuhahahaha!

Memimi: (I'm really sorry... But I'm not in a position to
worry about the talent... Can I even walk in public after
this...? From now on...!)

Cerberus Octopus: Well, I didn't expect it to actually
happen... It was a miscalculation, but... oh well, it's good
that I set it to record...

Henchman: Is this chick high on drugs or something? She did
an uncensored fuck on live TV for all of Japan to see!!
Exposing her ass and everything... She's finished as a
woman!

Underling: Hey, you! Insulting Lord Shark Duke is
unforgivable!! Getting all hard down there... We are too,
but...

Memimi: (Stop it... I'm starting to feel like crying
again... Even if I take back the organization, what I've
lost won't return... Ahh... no good... If I say one more
word, they'll notice I'm about to cry... I'm going to break
down...)

Bunny-chan: So with that, Lord Shark Duke has cleared the
challenge, which means a rematch is confirmed for the next
Monster Fight! Let's meet again at the venue~❤︎

Shark Broccoli: We shall go as well... We will obey as usual
until the day of the match, but don't push us too hard so it
doesn't affect our condition.

Cerberus Octopus: Tch, can't be helped! The free blowjob
campaign didn't work out too well either, so I guess I'll
sell the footage from earlier and think of a new strategy!

Memimi: Huh, huu... I managed not to cry... My dignity is...
somehow intact...
